{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1613631879.8521025", "card_id": "Q_444740522", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 329}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国得州遭遇冬季风暴，超 400 万人遭遇停电，8 千剂新冠疫苗受影响，还有哪些信息值得关注?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "14 日夜间，美国南部得克萨斯州部分地区开始遭遇冬季风暴，造成路面结冰、道路被封以及大面积停电。美联社 15 日称，由于低温导致用电需求暴增，该州超 400 万人遭遇停电。得州电力可靠性委员会一名官员表示，此次天气是「史无前例的」。停电还影响了休斯敦一个存储了 8000 剂新冠疫苗的设施，当地卫生官员正在紧急寻找疫苗接种者，以免造成疫苗浪费。美国得州风暴造成大面积停电 8 千剂新冠疫苗受影响"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-a5417f7c45245a0518fe3c7c01c09c46_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1331 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444740522"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItbrhiPio0/1xEAMaCDYxMTA5Nzk4IMbDroEGMDA4gwpAAHIJNDQ0NzQwNTIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1613631879.852826", "card_id": "Q_444673444", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1448}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大年初二，我回娘家，我爸爸妈妈给我弟弟的孩子 1000 元压岁钱，给我的孩子 100 元压岁钱，我该怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-8c7657924fd18d5b5d30d6d2700359e8_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "844 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444673444"}}, "attached_info": "CkAItbrhiPio0/1xEAMaCDYxMDk0OTYwIPzJrIEGMIYBOMwWQAFyCTQ0NDY3MzQ0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1613631879.8532405", "card_id": "Q_444639133", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 255}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么《你好，李焕英》开头李焕英不认女儿？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": " "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-1228b81ca233c2c4cb5e11449fba9931_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "655 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B730